_sText:
Description:
A medium sized snowy deathmatch map revamped with the suggestions from version 1.

Features:
- 3d skybox
- Snowfall
- Fog
- 30 spawn points
- point_spotlights
- Buyzones
- .NAV file
- HDR available

Updates:
- Added HDR
- Brightened
- Changed theme to snowy
- Added another building
- Fixed ladders
- Added more ways to get up on the crossroads
